What's the big deal, you wonder? It's a simple matter of giving
them a shampoo treatment and running a load or two of laundry. Hah.
Getting rid of head lice takes more time and energy than Brownie
troop, soccer meets and choir practice combined. These microscopic
pests can and will turn your household upside down. John Kessler
shares his experience. (Husted, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 20.
