<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-02 11:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8636 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CPT-COMPUTER-BYTES-HN     12-02 2920
