</P>
<P>
   GENOCIDE-MINISTER (Laredo, Texas) _ A federal judge has again
ordered an aging former clergyman be handed over to an
international war crimes tribunal on charges he led the slaughter
of dozens of people in Rwanda in 1994. Former Attorney General
Ramsey Clark, the elderly man's defense attorney, plans to appeal
the decision. By DANE SCHILLER.
