<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-02 18:50 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9678 &Cx1f; tad-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MICROSOFT-12-03-COX     12-02 0642
