 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    HEDGE YOUR BETS. With currencies teetering throughout the
region, companies across Latin America are protecting themselves
from fluctuations in the market. Lessons from the past may serve as
a guide. Just ask Brazil's Varig Airlines.
 &HT;    Filed as BC-CURRENCY-HEDGING-LATINTRADE-NYTSF.
