occupancy, through March 15, from Tourlite International, including
round-trip flights from New York on Delta Air Lines. Five nights'
lodging with daily buffet breakfast, service charge and taxes at
the deluxe Divani Palace Hotel, a classical Athens and museum tour
by bus and an escorted walking tour of the Plaka district are also
included.
</P>
<P>
   Departures are Thursday, Saturday and Sunday. Airport taxes and
fees totaling $77 are extra, and the program is not available Dec.
12 to 24. Information and reservations: (800) 272-7600 outside New
York City, or (212) 599-2727. &QL; 
 &QL;
