Passport that offers savings of up to 50 percent through March 31
at 100 hotels worldwide. The discounts are good for bookings of two
or more nights; the rates are for single or double occupancy, and
include tax and service charge.
</P>
<P>
   The special nightly rate is $90 at Le Meridien Nirwana in Bali;
$80 at Le Meridien Pyramids in Giza, and about $145 at Le Meridien
Nice (where the rate varies slightly depending on the exchange
