Kansas State was hurt by Texas A&AMP;M's embarrassing loss to Texas
last week. Still, the Wildcats can theoretically leapfrog UCLA with
a big victory or hope the Bruins stumble in Miami. Otherwise,
they're prepared to be bitter on Sunday.
</P>
