   &QL; 
 &UR; HOLIDAY ELECTRONICS/PERSONAL TECH PACKAGE &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR;  &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR; COOLGIFTS &LR;  _ Some holiday gifts are so hot, they're cool.
</P>
<P>
   We took a look at the computers and related electronics
available this year and picked out a few items that stand out for
their style and performance. Price also was a consideration _ we
didn't include anything beyond the means of the average
computer-geek consumer. By David Einstein
</P>
<P>
   &UR; RIO _ &LR;  OK, I confess, I admit my guilt. Call the cops, call the
D.A.
</P>
<P>
   Call the Recording Industry Association of America.
</P>
<P>
   My crime? I'm listening to an MP3 version of Madonna's ``Ray of
Light'' that I downloaded from a pirate Web site into one of
Diamond Multimedia's new $199 Rio PMP300 players. By Benny
Evangelista
</P>
<P>
   &UR; RIOSIDE _  &LR; Here's a quick glance at what the MP3 format is and
how it works. By Benny Evangelista
</P>
<P>
   &UR; RIOSITES _  &LR; Locating those darn copyright-infringing, illegal
