brought out some just to relax on the beach which is usually empty
in December. There are 23 shopping days left before Christmas,
however you wouldn't know it with temperatures in the Northeast
reaching 60 degrees Fahrenheit, some 20 degrees above normal.
(Keith Meyers/New York Times Photo)
